<p>Everybody knows <span style=" color: #ED1C24;">that</span> money doesn't grow on trees.</p>
<p>The dealer told me <span style=" color: #ED1C24;">(</span>how much he was prepared to pay for my car<span style=" color: #ED1C24;">)</span> and <span style=" color: #ED1C24;">that</span> I could have the money without delay.</p>
