<p>that 从句不能放在介词之后</p>
<p>He boasted about his success ==&#62; He boasted <span style=" color: #ED1C24;">that</span> he was successful.</p>
<p>但在疑问词开头的名词从句之前,介词则不可省去.</p>
<p>He boasted <span style=" color: #ED1C24;">about</span> <span style=" color: #ED1C24;">how</span> successful he was.</p>
